cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.DS 

This paper is about using neuro-evolution to investigate and evolve recurrent neural network memory structures. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves machine learning and statistical analysis, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of RNNs for time series prediction could also fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
